onnaissances en la matière. Les requis en mathématiques et en physique sont ceux des écoles d'ingénieurs et d'université (premier cycle). Des exercices sont proposés, avec leurs corrigés.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aAcoustical engineering. 0aAmplifiers (Electronics). 0aElectro-acoustics. 4aGeneral Physics. 7aSCIENCE / Physics / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102411008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2001 - 2015z978311075641840uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-0186-240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759801862423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759801862/original  a978-3-11-075641-8  EDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2001 - 2015c2001d2015  a978-3-11-102411-0  EDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2008d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK